title: Les Annales
additional-notes: This entry is for contribution renewal records listed as being from 'Les Annales' or 'Paris Annales', that are not from the 'Annales. Histoire, Science Sociales' titles.  There were multiple Parisian publications known as 'Annales' in this time period. All renewals mentioning such publications that have been filed before automatic renewals began have expired as of 2026.

The publications(s) referred to here are most likely French.  Their contents, therefore, may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US.
